# Data preprocessing
## checking for duplicates

```{r}
duplicated(irisdf)
```

## checking for missing value

```{r}
is.na(irisdf)
```

```{r}
sum(is.na(irisdf))
```

### imputation of missing values using the mean values
```{r}
irisdf$Petal.Width[is.na(irisdf$Petal.Width)]<-mean(irisdf$Petal.Width,na.rm = TRUE)
```
## imputatation of missing value using the median value
```{r}
irisdf_imputed <- irisdf %>% mutate(across(where(is.numeric), ~ ifelse(is.na(.), median(., na.rm = TRUE), .)))
```

