##predictive modeling 
##data spliting

```{r}
set.seed(123)
```

```{r}
trainSize<-round(nrow(irisdf)*0.7) 
testSize<-nrow(irisdf)-trainSize

```

```{r}
trainSize
testSize
```

```{r}
training_indices<-sample(seq_len(nrow(irisdf)),size =trainSize)
trainSet<-irisdf[training_indices,]
testSet<-irisdf[-training_indices,] 

```

```{r}
trainSet
```

```{r}
testSet
```

##training the model
```{r}
Sl_model<-lm(Sepal.Length~ Sepal.Width, trainSet)
```

```{r}
summary(Sl_model)
```

```{r}
Sl_model
```
